            <li class="prog-slot"><span class="prog-time">11:00</span><span class="prog-title">Ilya Boytsov — Fundamentals of LLMs · coding</span></li>
            <li class="prog-slot"><span class="prog-time">14:00</span><span class="prog-title">Research — introduction to project</span></li>
            <li class="prog-slot"><span class="prog-time">16:00</span><span class="prog-title">Ray Duch — Synthetic Agents for Benchmarking Experiments</span></li>
