            <li class="prog-slot"><span class="prog-time">14:00</span><span class="prog-title">Research</span></li>
            <li class="prog-slot"><span class="prog-time">16:00</span><span class="prog-title">Joan Timoneda — Using LLMs to Identify Overt and Covert Racism in Spanish</span></li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="prog-day">
          <div class="prog-day-head">
