          </div>
          <ol class="prog-slots">
            <li class="prog-slot"><span class="prog-time">09:15</span><span class="prog-title">Grigory Sapunov — AI Agents</span></li>
            <li class="prog-slot"><span class="prog-time">11:00</span><span class="prog-title">Sergei Skvortsov — LLM Fine-Tuning · coding</span></li>
            <li class="prog-slot"><span class="prog-time">14:00</span><span class="prog-title">Brandon Stewart — <a href="https://metrics-and-models.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Metrics &amp; Models seminar</a></span></li>
